<h2 id="the-reactjs-app">The ReactJS App <a class="headerlink" href="reactjs-api#the-reactjs-app" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>This is a small ReactJS app that uses our API to build all of the same markup that
we had on the page before, but dynamically. It uses jQuery to make the AJAX call:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="bde76dcba0">
