	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2949460999" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2949460999" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>A bit late in the game but I just did this course and really enjoyed it. I had the same error. This was caused by not having your data as an associative array named 'notes' in getNotesAction() of the controller.</p><p>So, instead of :</p><p>$data = [  $notes ];</p><p>It has to be:</p><p>$data = [ 'notes' =&gt; $notes ];</p><p>This is correct in the 'finish' code.</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
