	                                <p>Mybe you're using the response methode withe the json_encode function like this :<br>$response = new Response(json_encode($data,JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE));</p><p>In this case you should set the content type this way :<br>$response-&gt;headers-&gt;set('Content-Type', 'application/json');</p><p>If you don't the ajax response won't parse as json then notes won't be defined.</p><p>I had the same problem and fixed it as I mentionned !</p><p>Cheers !</p>
